name: Incoming NR IRAT Handover
summary: This feature makes it possible for a call arriving from an NR cell to be transferred to

parameters.name: INTERNAL_PROC_HO_PREP_S1_IN
parameters.description: Indicates the RAT of the source for incoming handover, or target                                     for outgoing handover cell.  EVENT_VALUE_NR enum value is introduced for incoming handover                                     from NR.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_PROC_HO_PREP_S1_IN
parameters.description: The result of the Handover Preparation Procedure.   EVENT_VALUE_FAILED_LICENSE_NR_HANDOVER enum value is introduced                                     for handover reject due to lack of Incoming NR IRAT handover                                     feature license.

events.name: INTERNAL_PROC_HO_PREP_S1_IN
events.description: Indicates the RAT of the source for incoming handover, or target                                     for outgoing handover cell.  EVENT_VALUE_NR enum value is introduced for incoming handover                                     from NR.

events.name: INTERNAL_PROC_HO_PREP_S1_IN
events.description: The result of the Handover Preparation Procedure.   EVENT_VALUE_FAILED_LICENSE_NR_HANDOVER enum value is introduced                                     for handover reject due to lack of Incoming NR IRAT handover                                     feature license.

activation_step: 1. Set the FeatureState.featureState attribute to ACTIVATED in the FeatureState=CXC4012385 MO instance.
deactivation_step: 1. Set the FeatureState.featureState attribute to DEACTIVATED in the FeatureState=CXC4012385 MO instance.
